    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a great project or a dependable work car for someone willing to put in a little effort. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable dents, some paint fading on the roof and hood, and a few areas of surface rust. Inside, the upholstery has some significant wear and a few tears, though the cabin remains functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will soon require attention to the suspension and a tune-up to ensure long-term reliability. It\u2019s a solid, honest vehicle that reflects its years on the road.",
      "price": 22500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
